## Implementation Notes

1. **Copy the entire @graph block** for your page type into a `<script type="application/ld+json">` tag in your page's `<head>`.
2. **Replace all [UPPERCASE-BRACKETS]** with real values from the business or page content.
3. **FAQPage answers must match page FAQ content exactly** — if FAQ text changes, update the schema.
4. **Breadcrumb paths must be correct** — verify each URL exists before shipping.
5. **Test all schema** with Google's Rich Results Test before deploying: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results
6. **LocalBusiness and Service blocks** must use the same phone number and address as the footer and Google Business Profile.

