## Placeholder Key

| Placeholder | Example | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `[DOMAIN]` | peterboroughplumbers.co.uk | Production domain only, no www |
| `[REAL-NUMBER]` | 01733456789 | Real, dialable UK number |
| `[EMAIL]` | hello@peterboroughplumbers.co.uk | Real contact email |
| `[STREET]` | 123 Main Street | Full street address from footer |
| `[POSTCODE]` | PE1 1XX | Business postcode |
| `[AREA-SLUG]` | bretton | Kebab-case area name |
| `[SERVICE-SLUG]` | boiler-repair | Kebab-case service name |
| `[REVIEW-COUNT]` | 47 | Actual review count on Google |
| `[FAQ-QUESTION-N]` | "What's your call-out fee?" | Exact question from page FAQ |
| `[FAQ-ANSWER-N]` | "From £49, waived if you book." | Exact answer from page FAQ |
| `[POST-SLUG]` | how-to-fix-leaky-tap | Kebab-case blog post slug |
| `[PUBLISHED-DATE-ISO]` | 2026-02-24T09:00:00Z | ISO 8601 format |
| `[LAST-MODIFIED-DATE-ISO]` | 2026-02-24T14:30:00Z | ISO 8601 format |
| `[FOUNDING-YEAR]` | 1993 | Year business started |
| `[PAGE]` | peterboroughplumbers | Facebook page slug |

